To John and William,<br><br>
Your collective observations that this thread does not contribute to the &quot;value&quot; of this site is probably shared by many. It is, however, a reaction, a collective outrage at one or more individuals who are peculiarly motivated to disrupt the process of civil discussion and debate of points. If you think this thread is bad, try a few back up the line for a real treat, and witness some of the spontaneous foul mouthed garbage that gushes from some very sick minds in a premeditated, destructive manner. The Ebola virus is a better, more predicatble friend than they.<br><br>
Concerning the term &quot;Cybergook&quot;, it really fits those who engage in pointless, outrageous, disruptive, and intollerable behavior here. As a coined word, it is much less &quot;offensive&quot; than the individuals it characterizes.<br><br>
I like it.<br>

